opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 21st day of December, 2015, the Application for Leave to File Original Petition is GRANTED, and the Application for an Immediate Hearing and the Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus are DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
